Class RpcSessionImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.rpc.RpcSessionImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RpcServiceLookup, RpcSession

    public class RpcSessionImpl
extends Object
implements RpcSession
    An abstract implementation for RpcSession which delegates #resolveClass(ObjectStreamClass) calls to #getClassByName(String).
